@startuml
title MicroMeet - Activity Diagram (Edit Meetup)

start
:1. Open Edit Meetup screen;
:2. System loads existing meetup details;
:3. Host updates fields (time/location/capacity/description);
:4. Host taps "Save";
:5. System validates changes;

if (Changes valid?) then (Yes)
  :6. System loads meetup;
  :7. System applies updates;
  :8. System updates location if changed;
  :9. System saves updated meetup;
  :10. System notifies participants;
  :11. Show "Meetup updated" confirmation;
else (No)
  :12. Show validation errors;
  :13. Host revises changes;
endif

stop

legend bottom
Steps mapping (numbers match actions):
1 Open edit meetup screen
2 Load existing meetup details
3 Update fields
4 Tap Save
5 Validate changes
6 Load meetup
7 Apply updates
8 Update location if changed
9 Save updated meetup
10 Notify participants
11 Show confirmation
12 Show validation errors
13 Revise changes
endlegend

@enduml